<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Opportunity Notification</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00b4ff 0%, #ffe066 100%); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center; }
        .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .user-info { background: #e8f4fd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 15px 0; }
        .opportunity { background: #fff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #00b4ff; }
        .footer { text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 20px; }
        .highlight { color: #00b4ff; font-weight: bold; }
        .action-button { display: inline-block; background-color: #00b4ff; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 15px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ðŸ†• New Opportunity Notification</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello Administrator,</h2>
            
            <p>A RH user has created a new opportunity and marked it for your immediate attention.</p>
            
            <div class="user-info">
                <h3>ðŸ‘¤ RH User Information:</h3>
                <p><strong>Name:</strong> {{ rh_user.name ?? 'Not specified' }}</p>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{ rh_user.email }}</p>
                <p><strong>Role:</strong> RH</p>
                <p><strong>Creation Date:</strong> {{ "now"|date("Y-m-d H:i:s") }}</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="opportunity">
                <h3>ðŸ“‹ New Opportunity Details:</h3>
                {% if opportunities|length > 0 %}
                    {% set opportunity = opportunities[0] %}
                    <p><strong>Name:</strong> <span class="highlight">{{ opportunity.name }}</span></p>
                    <p><strong>Company:</strong> {{ opportunity.company }}</p>
                    <p><strong>Contact Person:</strong> {{ opportunity.contact }}</p>
                    <p><strong>Value:</strong> {{ opportunity.value }} DT</p>
                    <p><strong>Deadline:</strong> {{ opportunity.closeDate|date("Y-m-d") }}</p>
                    {% if opportunity.description %}
                        <p><strong>Description:</strong> {{ opportunity.description }}</p>
                    {% endif %}
                {% endif %}
            </div>
            
            <p><strong>Action Required:</strong> Please log into the system to review this new opportunity.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated notification from the HR Management System.</p>
            <p>Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>